# Proud gymnast
Rowan was so proud to get his orange medal at gymnastics tonight\. After the Easter holidays he will be moving up to the next group\. He feels a little anxious about it but I think he is looking forward to advancing his skills\.

![](dayone-moment://8D39899245A5404EA4FABB4205C3B4FE)

Alan and I both think he looks a lot like Uncle Dan in this photo\.
